{"tid":1535631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你地跳閘啦！好唔好意思呀你老母？","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:14:57.000Z","uid":79965,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3df5fdc584074b361ead86cbf521455e6d44ee","tid":1535631,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"利申我知有時會驚，但係831 之後我已經無試過拍卡搭鐵<br />\n著便服跳，<br />\n隔離無人跳，<br />\n著西裝跳，<br />\n繁忙時間都跳。<br />\n有試過有個呀叔問我，「先生你做咩唔比錢呀？」，我望一望佢，頭也不回就走左。<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地多D同身邊朋友講。跳閘唔係我地唔文明，而係：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 港鐵同黑警狼狽為奸，傷害無辜市民，導致太子恐襲發生。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 港鐵一直未能對市民負責。太子恐襲無cctv唔講，點解可以無緣無故停東涌香港綫？點解可以夜晚無啦啦停曬三色線？點解可以因為合法集會而提早停港鐵？黨鐵無法為市民服務。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 黨鐵係香港係壟斷鐵路業，而且係政府作為大股東，市民無法問責。唔好同我講唔鍾意咪唔好搭/ 一件事還一件事。黨鐵無資格收市民一分一毫。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a766c33c8d10a95d5dfb2fc49c3dc9c9feca22c0","tid":1535631,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"你地鍾意組隊就組隊跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637f0d8581d71cb591bb7fc93643198c55720411","tid":1535631,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"組唔到就去我附近跳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064ea17d28ae43e18086be6bcc8893d2f566d204","tid":1535631,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"附近有人跳就跟住跳啦知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389286957831fc8ba48e9f3887adef8c806bd6ea","tid":1535631,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"四連"},{"pid":"8a927a0a794caa48d80741992bad235fbb02ef3c","tid":1535631,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite